<p>What is the solution to <m>\displaystyle{9}{x}+{2}={7}{x}+{4}</m>? <input type="text" style="width:4.6ch" name="qn0" id="qn0" value="" autocomplete="off" aria-label="Question 1" class="text"/> Â  </p>


