<solution>
<p><ul><li>1</li></ul></p><p><m>\displaystyle{9}{x}+{2}={7}{x}+{4}</m>.</p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{9}{x}+{2}-{4}={7}{x}+{4}-{4}</m>.</p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{9}{x}-{2}={7}{x}</m>.</p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{9}{x}-{2}-{9}{x}={7}{x}-{9}{x}</m>.</p>
<p><m>\displaystyle-{2}=-{2}{x}</m>.</p>
<p><m>\displaystyle-\frac{{2}}{{-{{2}}}}=\frac{{-{2}{x}}}{{-{{2}}}}</m>.</p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{1}={x}</m>.</p>

